Everyone must leave the Tunnel immediately.

01:47:17.760 --> 01:47:19.444
Attention, all units.

01:47:19.680 --> 01:47:22.047
Everybody must leave the Tunnel now.

01:47:28.520 --> 01:47:29.965
- Evacuate.
